section Section1;
shared Inventory_Velocity = let
  Source = Oracle.Database("COHREP", [HierarchicalNavigation=true, 
  Query="
 SELECT
    to_date(al1.date_run) - 1                    snapshot_date,
    al1.period_year * 100 + al1.fiscal_week_id run_id,
    (
        SELECT
            MAX(period_date)
        FROM
            (
                SELECT
                    gdpm.period_set_name,
                    gp.period_name,
                    gdpm.accounting_date                                                                             period_date,
                    gp.period_year,
                    gp.period_num,
                    gp.quarter_num,
                    gp.year_start_date,
                    gp.quarter_start_date,
                    ( gp.period_year * 100 + ceil((gdpm.accounting_date - gp.year_start_date + 1) / 7) )             week_series
                FROM
                    gl.gl_date_period_map    gdpm,
                    gl.gl_periods            gp
                WHERE
                        gdpm.period_set_name = 'COHR Calendar'
                    AND gp.period_name = gdpm.period_name
                    AND gdpm.period_set_name = gp.period_set_name
            ) cal
        WHERE
            cal.week_series = al1.period_year * 100 + al1.fiscal_week_id
    ) run_id_date,
    al1.me_flag,
    al1.freeze_data,
    al1.osp_assemblies,
    al1.planning_method,
    al1.organization_code,
    al1.item_number,
    al1.item_description,
    al1.uom,
    al1.item_status,
    al1.item_type,
    nvl(SUBSTR(al1.current_mrp_abc_class,1,1), 'Blank')        current_abc_class,       
    CASE
        WHEN al1.org_tbu IS NULL THEN
            NULL
        ELSE
            al1.org_tbu
            || '.'
            || al1.org_family
            || '.'
            || al1.org_line
            || '.'
            || al1.org_forecast_field
    END org_product,
    CASE
        WHEN al1.mas_tbu IS NULL THEN
            NULL
        ELSE
            al1.mas_tbu
            || '.'
            || al1.mas_family
            || '.'
            || al1.mas_line
            || '.'
            || al1.mas_forecast_field
    END mas_product,
    CASE
        WHEN al1.org_tbu IS NOT NULL THEN
            al1.org_tbu
            || '.'
            || al1.org_family
            || '.'
            || al1.org_line
            || '.'
            || al1.org_forecast_field
        WHEN al1.mas_tbu IS NOT NULL THEN
            al1.mas_tbu
            || '.'
            || al1.mas_family
            || '.'
            || al1.mas_line
            || '.'
            || al1.mas_forecast_field
        ELSE
            NULL
    END product_key,
    al1.planner,
    al1.buyer,
    al1.min_max_min_qty,
    al1.min_max_max_qty,
    al1.min_order_qty,
    al1.max_order_qty,
    al1.fixed_order_qty,
    al1.fixed_days_supply,
    al1.fixed_lot_size_multiplier,
    al1.acceptable_early_days,
    al1.processing_lead_time,
    al1.cumulative_mfg_lt,
    al1.cumulative_lt,
    CASE
        WHEN al1.planning_method = 'Min-Max' THEN
            al1.attribute_lt
        ELSE
            al1.active_supplier_lt
    END effective_lead_time,
    al1.active_supplier_lt,
    al1.purch_asl_lt,
    al1.subinventory_min_max_lt,
    al1.kanban_repl_lt,
    al1.total_gr_26_weeks,
    al1.average_daily_demand,
    al1.gross_inventory_turns,
    al1.item_cost,
    al1.currency_rate,
    al1.item_cost_usd,
    al1.sourcing_commodity,
    al1.sr_vendor,
    al1.sr_vendor_site_code,
    al1.sr_pct,
    al1.sr_asl_status,
    al1.sr_vndr_src_org,
    al1.safety_stock_qty,
    al1.safety_stock_value,
    al1.safety_stock_value_usd,
    al1.inventory_value,
    al1.inventory_value_usd,
    al1.receiving_quantity,
    al1.receiving_value,
    al1.receiving_value_usd,
    al1.intransit_quantity,
    al1.intransit_value,
    al1.intransit_value_usd,
    al1.total_quantity,
    al1.total_onhand_qty,
    al1.on_hand_days_of_supply,
    al1.open_po_qty,
    al1.open_po_value,
    al1.open_po_value_usd,
    al1.on_order_days_of_supply,
    al1.wip_in_process_qty,
    al1.wip_in_process_value,
    al1.wip_in_process_value_usd,
    al1.wip_days_of_supply,
    al1.total_days_of_supply,
    al1.proj_spend_next_26_weeks,
    al1.proj_spend_next_26_weeks_usd,
    al1.open_blankets,
    al1.number_of_open_blankets,
    al1.sum_remaining_amount,
    al1.sum_usd_remaining_amount,
    al1.sum_remaining_qty_calculated,
    al1.blanket_days_supply_remaining,
    al1.active_or_inactive,
    al1.attribute_lt,
    al1.onhand_qty_non_asset,
    al1.onhand_qty_asset,
    al1.ir_po_qty,
    al1.ir_po_value,
    al1.ir_po_value_usd,
    al1.onorder_po_qty,
    al1.onorder_po_value,
    al1.onorder_po_value_usd,
    al1.sr_vendor_site_id,
    al1.weekly_gross_reqs_week_0,
    al1.weekly_gross_reqs_week_1,
    al1.weekly_gross_reqs_week_2,
    al1.weekly_gross_reqs_week_3,
    al1.weekly_gross_reqs_week_4,
    al1.weekly_gross_reqs_week_5,
    al1.weekly_gross_reqs_week_6,
    al1.weekly_gross_reqs_week_7,
    al1.weekly_gross_reqs_week_8,
    al1.weekly_gross_reqs_week_9,
    al1.weekly_gross_reqs_week_10,
    al1.weekly_gross_reqs_week_11,
    al1.weekly_gross_reqs_week_12,
    al1.weekly_gross_reqs_week_13,
    al1.weekly_gross_reqs_week_14,
    al1.weekly_gross_reqs_week_15,
    al1.weekly_gross_reqs_week_16,
    al1.weekly_gross_reqs_week_17,
    al1.weekly_gross_reqs_week_18,
    al1.weekly_gross_reqs_week_19,
    al1.weekly_gross_reqs_week_20,
    al1.weekly_gross_reqs_week_21,
    al1.weekly_gross_reqs_week_22,
    al1.weekly_gross_reqs_week_23,
    al1.weekly_gross_reqs_week_24,
    al1.weekly_gross_reqs_week_25,
    al1.weekly_gross_reqs_week_26,
    al1.total_usage_26_weeks,
    al1.so_usage_13_weeks,
    al1.so_usage_26_weeks,
    al1.wo_usage_13_weeks,
    al1.wo_usage_26_weeks,
    al1.spc_usage_volume_13_weeks_usd,
    al1.ave_daily_usage_26_weeks,
    al1.kanban_type,
    al1.lt_grouping,
    al1.lt_grouping_id,
    al1.sec_reporting,
    al1.operations_reporting
FROM
    apps.xx_invascp_fact al1
WHERE
     al1.organization_code = '"&ORG&"'
       AND ( al1.me_flag = 'Y'
          OR al1.period_name = (
        SELECT
            gp.period_name
        FROM
            gl.gl_date_period_map    gdpm,
            gl.gl_periods            gp
        WHERE
                gdpm.period_set_name = 'COHR Calendar'
            AND gp.period_name = gdpm.period_name
            AND gdpm.period_set_name = gp.period_set_name
            AND gdpm.accounting_date = trunc(sysdate)
    ) )
    and al1.period_year >= (select period_year - "&YearOffset&"
    from gl.gl_periods            gp
where trunc(sysdate) between gp.start_date and gp.end_date
and period_set_name = 'COHR Calendar')
", CommandTimeout=#duration(0, 0, 10, 0)]),
